::Epyon:: 

He ran up to Prowl.
"My troops should be moving here soon, and bringing the scrap from the
StarJumper with them."

::Hot Rod::

He came along side Epyon.
"When we get start training, and if we get a chance of sparing, how
about you and me?"

::Epyon::

"No problem here."
